Package lab6

Class ToyList<T>

java.lang.Object
lab6.ToyList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type parameter representing the toy age group or category
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Toy<T>>, Collection<Toy<T>>, List<Toy<T>>
public class ToyList<T> extends Object implements List<Toy<T>>
A custom list implementation that stores Toy objects. The list is backed by a dynamically resized array that increases its capacity by 30% when it becomes full.
